Apple Inc. was founded in the year 1976. The first CEO to lead the company was Michael Scott. Below is the LaTeX code to represent this information:

```latex
\documentclass{article}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\begin{document}

\textbf{Apple Inc. Founding Year and First CEO}

\begin{itemize}
    \item \text{Founding Year: } 1976
    \item \text{First CEO: } \text{Michael Scott}
\end{itemize}

\end{document}
```

This code will display the founding year and the first CEO of Apple Inc. when compiled in a LaTeX editor.
